Tywn sur Paendrag Paeron held the letter from the Lord Captain commander with a sneer on his face.

He had thought hard on this course of action. He did not truly believe this man was the Dragon Reborn; but what should be endured, could be.

>   Reimon Todande,

>   I will keep this missive short. 

>   I have recently come into possession of some information that i believe might be of interest to you.

>   It will be difficult to meet in person, and i would prefer not to put such sensitive words in ink.

>   It is said the stone will never fall until the People of the Dragon come. i like to think myself a scholar and have puzzled upon its meaning a lot. 
 
>   
